org.sql: SELECT articles.user_id FROM articles INNER JOIN (SELECT reactions.id, reactions.reactable_id, reactions.user_id FROM reactions WHERE reactions.user_id = 5379 AND reactions.category = 'readinglist' AND reactions.status IN ('confirmed', 'valid') AND reactions.reactable_type = 'Article' ORDER BY reactions.created_at DESC) AS reactions ON reactions.reactable_id = articles.id WHERE articles.published = "$1" AND published_at <= '2022-02-27 07:17:29.634659' LIMIT "$2" OFFSET "$3"
